{"tid":839794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉危駕撞死鐵騎士　1.5萬元保釋　下月提訊","createTime":"2018-09-28T08:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T08:16:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"768faa281b9553819dd442166006729a49f0844f","tid":839794,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"27歲休班警員涉於今年4月3日，在大埔公路沙田嶺段失控逆線，撞倒駕駛電單車的53歲男子，男子傷重不治。休班警被控危險駕駛引致他人死亡，案件今在沙田裁判法院提堂。裁判官押後至下月26日提訊，處理案件轉介至區域法院的文件，被告獲准以1.5萬元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，報稱公務員的被告唐建偉（27歲）於本年4月3日，在沙田大埔公路沙田嶺段近燈柱位置，危險駕駛引致林日安死亡。"},{"pid":"f6adfe9aba0820e0d7eed4c3188337017e2c78b4","tid":839794,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180928/s00001/1538120829788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180928%2Fs00001%2F1538120829788&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa088n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=863ccff0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180928%2Fs00001%2F1538120829788&h=14af57c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180928/s00001/1538120829788</a>"},{"pid":"3c046d4556f1739008fc17f516f5726f0cafcae1","tid":839794,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"休班警又一分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}